{"tid":1009700,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"隻貓教咗兩年仲不斷喺床痾尿","createTime":"2019-02-05T11:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T17:55:39.000Z","uid":96402,"like":6,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"fa72e1d63c71a7e7776371ba2b21c810499bdb6c","tid":1009700,"uid":96402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T11:17:54.000Z","msg":"好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 教咗兩年都係咁<br />\n屋又搬過 所有google出現嘅解決方法都試過<br />\nPo塊膠喺床上面都試過比佢捐到入去痾<br />\n打又試過 鬧又試過 唔打唔鬧都試過<br />\n都係繼續痾 痾足兩年 一個月洗幾次床<br />\n屋企地方有限 冇辦法唔比佢喺房<br />\n因為廳有隻狗<br />\n隻貓貓女黎 今年一歲幾<br />\n發咗一排情 之前喺街執返黎的<br />\n前排幫佢絕咗育<br />\n真係好絕望 再教唔到嘅話<br />\n屋企人話會將佢送走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"871d1ad5c2e52a456d03436d59f4957a740ec88f","tid":1009700,"uid":9411,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T11:22:04.000Z","msg":"po左圖先有人答你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a409e4cd81f181722a0ccc134b35eb8767c90f","tid":1009700,"uid":14494,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T11:23:05.000Z","msg":"你去番佢張床痾尿"},{"pid":"7e73faf192dbd3f92d9a88f055faa71c2aca5dd3","tid":1009700,"uid":17535,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T11:26:09.000Z","msg":"一歲幾但教咗兩年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4784749d262cd194d82f9f5745ea5a84b0adecf7","tid":1009700,"uid":167878,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T11:32:11.000Z","msg":"養唔熟<br />\n唯有煮熟佢"},{"pid":"781c0f3427b9b0678befb6b05f304743d8f5b4d2","tid":1009700,"uid":192105,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T11:43:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b37e5c71a0ad238597bf0d63619bfa784c88fa9","tid":1009700,"uid":214416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e73faf192dbd3f92d9a88f055faa71c2aca5dd3","tid":1009700,"uid":17535,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":3,